 services, higher medical costs, and rates of emergency department use. \n\nTime Points Item(s) Completed \n\n\u2022  Start of Care \n\nOASIS-E1 \nEffective 01/01/2025 \nCenters for Medicare & Medicaid Services \n\n55", "type": "Document"}}